npm init -y
npm install -D tailwindcss@3
npx tailwindcss init
tailwind.config.js



🚀 STEP 3 — Configure tailwind.config.js

Open tailwind.config.js and replace everything with:

module.exports = {
  content: [
    "./*.php",
    "./**/*.php",
  ],
  theme: {
    extend: {},
  },
  plugins: [],
}


🚀 STEP 4 — Create CSS Structure

Create folders:

src/
dist/


Inside src, create file:

input.css


Add inside input.css:

@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

🚀 STEP 5 — Build Tailwind

Run this:

npx tailwindcss -i ./src/input.css -o ./dist/output.css --watch


Now it will generate:

dist/output.css


Leave this running while developing.

